Speaker 2: Absolutely. Well, it was nice catching up with you. I should get going, got a project deadline looming.
Speaker 1: Good luck with that, I'm sure you'll nail it. Let's catch up again soon.
Speaker 2: Sounds great. Have a good day!
Speaker 1: You too, take care!
